  "2026-06-26T04:22:12.908Z",claude-code-agent,"Status audit 2026-06-26 (claude-code-agent): every sub-item of this completion Plan is now closed/shipped — pm-k8ik (remove-type), pm-e77a (add-status), pm-f4r1 (per-type workflows), pm-jpwo (config create_default_type), pm-mt7k (schema list/show), pm-vhd9 (init --type-preset). The parent epic pm-8jdc is at 22/24 closed. This Plan is functionally complete and is a candidate for a dedicated governance-close pass (kept open here to avoid mixing a release-changelog regeneration trigger into an unrelated code PR, per pm-j8z6's bundling guidance)."
